Summary: planner-erc: Improve greatly.
Keywords: 

* planner-erc.el: Update the syntax for IRC URLs.  Add warning for users
  of old versions of ERC.
  (planner-erc-url-regexp): New variable that specifies the syntax of IRC
  URLs.
  (planner-erc-annotation-from-erc): Use `erc-server-announced-name'.
  (planner-erc-browse-url): Figure out the desired chat buffer.  If no
  chat buffer exists for the given URL, connect to the server.
